title: Ep. 733 - Tapu Wants To Star In A Movie - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: It's a casual day at the Jethalal household when Tapu dresses up as a hero and surprises his family. He makes everyone know that he wishes to star in a movie and nags Jetha to get him into the same!

title: Ep. 734 - Iyer Brings Presents For Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita tells Iyer that they must do something for Jetha and Daya as they have done a lot for them. Hence, as a token of appreciation Iyer brings presents for all of them, making Jetha suspect him much more than before!

title: Ep. 735 - Popatlal Takes A Chance  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popat receives a mysterious call from a woman and gets excited that maybe it's his luck that is trying to set him up with her. Upon believing the same, he takes a chance!

title: Ep. 736 - Dr. Haathi And Popat Get Into A Brawl - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dr. Haathi and Popat get into a huge quarrel where they pass personal comments at each other, getting everyone tensed on how things might escalate! Watch to find out about why they got into a tiff!

title: Ep. 737 - Making Amends - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal falls sick and acts stubborn on not going and visiting Dr. Haathi due to the fight they had. All the residents pursue him to go and get checked, and hence they make amends.

title: Ep. 738 - Popatlal Gets A Shocking News - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popat acts friendlier than usual to Dr. Haathi as it comes to his notice that, a friend has visited him and has a daughter who's a bachelor and wants to tie some sort of relationship with her. Watch to find out how he gets a shock!

title: Ep. 739 - Bhide Bans Tapu Sena From Playing - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide gets infuriated on Tapu Sena's behavior that has caused inconvenience to quite a lot due to their outdoor games and arrives at a strict conclusion that he must ban them from playing games if there's peace to be restored in the society.

title: Ep. 740 - Tapu Sena's Families Take Strict Measures - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the residents take their respective child and try to teach them a lesson about how mischievious they've become and try to arrive at a conclusion that benefits both the children and the parents.

title: Ep. 741 - Daya Is Worried For Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is supposed to go to the airport. However, he does not reach and there is Daya panics. People around tell her that he will be safe but she refuses to believe and calls up Nattu Kaka to check.

title: Ep. 742 - Jetha's Police Encounter - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The thieves come to Jetha's godown where he is stuck. Jetha tells them to back off and leave his stuff untouched. They scare him and try stealing his electronics when the police arrive and Jetha tells them the truth.

title: Ep. 743 - A Wrong Number - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya and the family visit the police officer to ask about any updates on Jetha's location. Jetha meanwhile gives away all the information about his shop and the godown to the thieves in the lock-up.

title: Ep. 744 - Daya's Idea To Stop The Thieves - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu sees that there are some thieves at Jetha's godown and decides to stop them. Daya decides to scare them as a ghost. As she is successful in her plan, she hopes to find Jetha as well.

title: Ep. 745 - Why Is Jetha Hiding? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha hides into the rickshaw as soon as Iyer and Babita see him. Listening to the chaos, everyone in society comes out to see what the unrest is about. Jetha finally tells everyone about the incidents of the previous night.

title: Ep. 746 - Bhide To Gift Madhavi Roses - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka visits Jetha after he comes home. Nattu kaka asks him how were they supposed to know Jetha was in the godown before locking it. Later, Bhide tells Madhavi that he will get roses for her.

title: Ep. 747 - The Importance Of An Umbrella - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide's umbrella is broken and hence he decides to discard it. Popatlal sees the broken umbrella being put away by Bhide and calls him heartless for doing such a thing.
